## Input Validation

All tool inputs are validated using Zod schemas:

```typescript
// Example from {{tool-name}}
{
  param1: z.string().max(1000).describe('...'),
  param2: z.number().min(0).max(100).describe('...'),
}
```

### Validation Rules

- String lengths are bounded
- Numbers are range-checked
- URLs are validated
- Paths are sanitized

